# Cloudflare Pages — URL rewrites.
#
# /admin/ is a single-page app. SPA shell routing is handled by a
# Pages Function at functions/admin/[[path]].js — it returns
# /admin/index.html for any /admin/<route>/ path, so refreshes
# don't 404.
#
# We tried the obvious _redirects approach first
# (`/admin/*  /admin/index.html  200`) and explicit per-route
# variants; CF's loop detector rejects both for trailing-slash
# sources, which are the only form the SPA actually uses. See
# the comment block in functions/admin/[[path]].js for the full
# story.
#
# This file is intentionally empty until we have a non-SPA
# redirect to set up.
